<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Hans und Georg von Streitberg</head><p>Der Rat bestätigt, dass Jobst Memminger, Bürger zu Nürnberg, nach seiner Freilassung in Nürnberg Urfehde geschworen hat.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_248" id="123v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_248_r1l1">Hanſen vnd Görgen von Streipperg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_248_r1l2"><expan>Lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Hans vnd Görg / . Als Jr Jobſen <expan>Memmyng<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r1l3"><expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>gevange<ex>n</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> het </del> vnd dem tag <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> het / . darvmb vvir <expan cert="unknown">H</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r1l4">Schollen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒü ew <expan>ſchıckt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / der vns geſagt hat / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r1l6">er cʒelecʒt darvmb <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew <expan>geſchıed<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſeÿ / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_248_line_1576582602732_3358">Alſo </ab></add> daʒ <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r1l7">ein vrfeh vor vns tun vnd domit der vanknüʒʒ ledig ſein ſolt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r1l8">wenn wir ew <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ er die vrfeh vor vns getan het </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r1l9">Alſo / <expan>laʒʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> vvıſſen / daʒ <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Jobs <expan>Mem<ex>m</ex>yng<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r1l10">von <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vanküʒʒ <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / ein ſlehte vrfeh vor vns getan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r1l11">vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒü </del> geſworn hat / . das fürbas nicht cʒe anden / <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_248_r1l12">deſt veinder cʒe ſein / . <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . </ab>
