<ab>Hansen und Görgen von Streipperg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Hans und Görg, als ir Jobsen
                                <expan>Memmyng<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>gevange<ex>n</ex></expan> und dem tag
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> het, darumb wir <expan cert="unknown">H.</expan> Schollen, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, czü ew <expan>schickt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        der uns gesagt hat, daz er czeleczt darumb <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> ew
                                <expan>geschied<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sey <add>also</add>, daz
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ein urfeh vor uns tun und domit der vanknüzz
                        ledig sein solt, wenn wir ew <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>,
                        daz er die urfeh vor uns getan het. Also <expan>lazze<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                        ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> wissen, daz
                            <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Jobs
                            <expan>Mem<ex>m</ex>yng<ex>er</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vanküzz <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        ein slehte urfeh vor uns getan und gesworn hat, das fürbas nicht cze anden
                                <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> dest veinder cze sein
                                <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.</ab>
</div>
